key_findings: Looking at the sources, the first two chunks are from q3_feedback_app. The third and fourth are from fraud_ops, which might not be relevant here. The fifth is enterprise_clients, which is also not related. So I should only consider the first two chunks.

Transfer flow has 7 steps with abandonment at confirmation increasing from 9% to 14% quarter-over-quarter.
Android 12 upload crash rate is 3.2% compared to 0.4% on iOS 17, mainly due to image uploads.
New user 7-day retention dropped from 38% to 31%.
